definition.value: Introduces a cis double bond at a location 3 carbons away from the methyl end of the fatty acid. Acts on all 16:2- or 18:2-containing chloroplast membrane lipids, including phosphatidylglycerol, monogalactosyldiacylglycerol, digalactosyldiaclyglycerol, and sulfoquinovosyldiacylglycerol.
